{
  "stem": "20616.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How the-- yes, he sold razor blades to the different candy stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he came home at night and said, you know, it's not bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The stores all buy them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened was-- well, let me continue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He sold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He went to different candy stores.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's supposed to follow up on those stores a week or two later to see-- to replenish the stock so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the first few days went very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He sold quite a few of these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then he went back to the stores to follow up on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the store keepers shook their heads.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They pointed to the razor blade cardboard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were still all there, said, I didn't sell any.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I can't keep buying them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he found out that they were mostly Jewish storekeepers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he-- they bought one carton out of pity, more or less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, you know, times being what they are-- by the way, in those candy stores, they didn't just sell candy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They sold everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was actually what a drugstore is today, what the big drug stores are like, only on a much smaller scale.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Stationery stores, newspapers, everything was sold in those candy stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he found out that after the first one, there was no market for it anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then he sold Fuller brushes, which Fuller brushes were sold from door-to-door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were very good brushes and very well-known brushes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they're mostly known for the free samples that they gave out to people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in fact, for years and years, he had free samples from Fuller Brush Men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But my father went to school there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
